Ibiti biritwararika cane ibidukikije, bigatuma birwanya ivyo gutikiza ubwoko bwavyo (na ho nyene ari bumwe).
Igihe ugiye gutembera mu busitani bw'imiterere, gutora "ibiti vy'akarorero" birashobora gutuma uheba ico gikorwa ata n'ico uvuze.
Singapore ni kimwe mu bihugu bitekanye cane, kandi iyo uvuyeyo urashobora kugura ikintu cose wipfuza, kandi biroroshe kuronka inzira.
Kubera ko iri mu "bibanza bishushe" biri hejuru gato y'umubumbe w'isi, urashobora guhura n'ubushuhe bwinshi n'izuba ryinshi (mu gihe uri hanze, nturike).
Hariho ibarabara rya kure rija mu buraruko rija i Heburoni, aho Aburahamu, Isaka, Yakobo n'abagore babo bahambwe, nk'uko bivugwa mu nyigisho za Yezu.
Rimbura kandi ko indege wibaza ko igenda mu gihugu ca Heburoni, kandi ko igenda mu kibanza Abayuda baba i Kiryat Arba.
Amazi yo mu mazinga arashobora kuba akaryo keza ko kuruhuka.
Nk'akarorero, urashobora gutembera mu nyubakwa z'amazu y'ibisagara ziri mu kiyaya ca Loire, mu kiyaya ca Rhine, canke ukaja gutembera mu bisagara vy'akaroruhore biri ku ruzi Danube canke ukaja gutembera mu bwato ku Mwonga Erie.
Barerekana inzira z'amabuye y'agaciro n'amabuye y'agaciro.
Noweli ni umusi mukuru uhambaye cane mu misi mikuru ya gikirisu, ukaba uhimbaza ivuka rya Yezu.
Imigenzo myinshi ijanye n'uwo musi mukuru yarakurikijwe n'abantu bo mu bihugu vy'abakirisu be n'abatari abakirisu.
Hari umugenzo wo kurara atagohetse mw'ijoro rya Pasika ahantu hatandukanye hagenewe kuraba izuba.
Ego ni ko, hariho insobanuro y'idini rya gikirisu kuri iyo migenzo, ariko birashoboka ko ari imigenzo ya gikirisu yo mu gihe c'ici, hamwe n'imisi mikuru yo gusaba umugisha.
Amadini ya gikirisu y'imigenzo yama ategura umusi mukuru wa Pasika ku mugoroba wo ku wa gatandatu mu ndwi ya Pasika, hamwe n'abakirisu bagirira umusi mukuru uwo mugoroba kugira ngo bahimbaze izuka rya Kristu.
